Package accounts

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Account
    The Account class is an abstract class, which acts as a framework for the Savings and Checking classes.
    AccountDatabase
    The AccountDatabase class manages the array of accounts in the system.
    AccountDatabaseTest
    The AccountDatabaseTest is a JUnit4 test specifically for the AccountDatabase class.
    Profile
    The Profile class holds all the identifications of a person needed to open accounts.
